<item>
            <title>[LU-7506] lfs quota -h should support petabytes output</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7506</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;lfs quota -h  &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;should support petabytes it currently only supports terabytes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Example&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;pfe23 ~ # lfs quota -h -u xxxxx /nobackupp8
Disk quotas &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; user xxxx (uid ####):
     Filesystem    used   quota   limit   grace   files   quota   limit   grace
    /nobackupp8   1576T   1863T   2049T       - 5942721  10000000 15000000
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
